{"tid":964442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獨派高舉八地獨立旗幟","createTime":"2019-01-01T10:20:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-17T12:37:50.000Z","uid":47359,"like":159,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"1d923493403c30ab7bfb496047825bd18d293826","tid":964442,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:20:34.000Z","msg":"[八地獨立遊行直擊]<br />\n14:10 遊行人士於記利佐治街集合<br />\n14:40 獨派同時高舉港獨及台獨旗<br />\n15:55 獨派同時高舉上海、東突厥、圖博（西藏）、滿州、南蒙古、巴蜀利亞（四川）獨立旗幟<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.independence.union/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.independence.union%2F&d=gU8nps7zQsY9NRt2s4Sj8I9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=70ecd00f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.independence.union/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X1vT7Wi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX1vT7Wi.png&h=b636d91b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YYSfBPD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYYSfBPD.png&h=992f3bf9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mf8ngPE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmf8ngPE.png&h=8d812905&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3793ce08421d60bd07bfddb49078e82b966cf006","tid":964442,"uid":176166,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:21:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28bcd1cbcd12153502976023f548143f58519a71","tid":964442,"uid":68610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:21:44.000Z","msg":"新年快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bdf243f72262a39307b9ecb7edd6b872f46bb0","tid":964442,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:22:16.000Z","msg":"無大越國？"},{"pid":"302854b0090d552e62c146a6815b483f3ca42586","tid":964442,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0037ec7b384635751261f624b74122151beada69","tid":964442,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:29:23.000Z","msg":"巴蜀利亞咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad0bf4de2cc7edff8bbfee6f3e1ff0acb911dd6","tid":964442,"uid":35790,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:29:56.000Z","msg":"諗起李登輝&ldquo;七塊論&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n台灣出了本李登輝的書，名為《台灣的主張》。書中一個引人注目的觀點就是&ldquo;中國七塊論&rdquo;。李登輝寫道：最理想的狀況，是中國大陸擺脫大中華主義的束縛，讓文化與發展的程度各不相同的地區享有充分的自主權。如<span style=\"color: red;\">台灣、西藏、新疆、蒙古、東北</span>等，大約分成七個區域，相互競爭，追求進步，亞洲或許會更安定。台灣的一家媒體在報導李氏&ldquo;中國七塊論&rdquo;時，冠以&ldquo;李登輝主張大卸中國一分為七&rdquo;的通欄標題，甚至還在中國地圖上以不同的色塊標出了這&ldquo;七塊&rdquo;，即除上述提到的五塊外，還有以<span style=\"color: red;\">長江為區隔的江北、江南兩塊。是為&ldquo;七塊&rdquo;</span>。"},{"pid":"3e7fd8d3d6abb36808357e0c91e600d3dbc088bd","tid":964442,"uid":38523,"like":20,"dislike":47,"score":-27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:32:32.000Z","msg":"舉完旗<br />\n叫完口號<br />\n就好快d番屋企用淘寶<br />\n買中資<br />\n去大陸做野啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本就係左膠遊行來<br />\n比位大家發排洩下就完場<br />\n你答我同泛民左膠遊行有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f5c10622627648834459ce9e6f33bfd8327408f","tid":964442,"uid":38523,"like":13,"dislike":18,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T10:34:34.000Z","msg":"泛民和平遊行就係左膠<br />\n大陸間碟關愛座hunter和平遊行就係做到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你出聲屌<br />\n你就係五毛<br />\n泛民左膠遊行<br />\n你唔去就正確<br />\n大陸間碟左膠遊行<br />\n你唔去就係淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b29d19d3d3be0cd39e565df542c2eba06f94fbf","tid":964442,"uid":149494,"like":2,"dislike":13,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"3e7fd8d3d6abb36808357e0c91e600d3dbc088bd","tid":964442,"uid":38523,"like":20,"dislike":47,"score":-27,"